behaves like a near-perfect lens. Overall,\nthese numerically simulated results could serve as useful approximations to the\ndegree of resonant amplification and refocusing of near-fields that can be\nachieved by flat superlens in near-fields experimental imaging setups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 12 Jan 2021 17:26:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-14"}
