ous\nmethods on both the seen test set and the unseen test set of the EPIC Kitchens\nAction Anticipation Challenge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2021 08:04:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jan 2021 11:02:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-20"}
