face, thus opening\nup a new route towards fiber-enhanced multifunctional structures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2021 15:05:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 23 Mar 2021 15:02:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-28"}
