D nanoobject proposed here can be considered as an\nexample of the general three-stage strategy of production of nanoobjects and\nmacromolecules. 1) precursors are synthesized by traditional chemical method,\n2) precursors are placed in HRTEM with the electron energy that is sufficient\nonly to remove hydrogen atoms, 3) as a result of hydrogen removal, the\nprecursors become unstable or metastable and transform into new nanoobjects or\nmacromolecules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2021 15:20:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-14"}
